{"tid":2255152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓：中國吹來的沙塵暴或帶武漢肺炎病毒 要求民眾留在室內","createTime":"2020-10-23T10:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T11:06:58.000Z","uid":21470,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"da66e3ddc64cee0dd8d67d9e61f4a50955b18c2e","tid":2255152,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"北韓警告民眾提防由中國吹來帶新冠病毒沙塵暴<br />\n<br />\n北韓警告民眾提防從中國吹來的「黃色粉塵」可能帶有新型冠狀病毒，要求他們留在室內。<br />\n<br />\n首都平壤星期四的街頭，據報基本上空無一人。<br />\n<br />\n北韓中央電視台星期三播出特別天氣報告，警告星期四將有「黃色粉塵」湧入，下令全國戶外建築工程停工。<br />\n<br />\n「黃色粉塵」是指季節性由蒙古和中國沙漠吹到南北韓的沙塵暴，長年以來夾雜有毒霧霾，危及南北韓民眾健康。<br />\n<br />\n北韓《勞動新聞》說，所有工人必須明確認識到病毒入侵的危險。<br />\n<br />\n在北韓的外國大使館亦據報收到平壤當局發出的警告。<br />\n<br />\n目前未有季節性沙塵暴與新型冠狀病毒之間的已知聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556338-20201023.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556338-20201023.htm&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=5ad4b5e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556338-20201023.htm&h=dbfa58b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556338-20201023.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7e679f27d5936d4c6fbc3da04ab613a70b7751d1","tid":2255152,"uid":5737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"北韓 你咁講咩意思<br />\n係咪姐係話肺炎係來自中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca7960935eb4dbdbcc00a7e9b74023247f3713c","tid":2255152,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:25:18.000Z","msg":"聰明"},{"pid":"8f3da83828533014ac96a5f536c52a12e15a660a","tid":2255152,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2550141c6ec16b454e24b46e0198f808292f493","tid":2255152,"uid":59328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"終於明白pokemon點解沙塵暴每回合扣血啦"},{"pid":"0fd112f2e5121b4bb10b6e8aace88d9338e226a8","tid":2255152,"uid":54125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:31:51.000Z","msg":"諗起 防疫我只服北韓 呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5083aec3cc5727194d7f3271deca9c66bb8b9c","tid":2255152,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88fd8ca35f957995d3b6ed047241d327cad0073","tid":2255152,"uid":343643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:50:13.000Z","msg":"防疫我只信金正恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e74377d4171048d11ec5f1a58a1436671450ed7","tid":2255152,"uid":363413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b0bf3cb19ea406a22a2e683586fda7e736aec0","tid":2255152,"uid":72749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itJxDqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitJxDqf.png&h=885defea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}